'Welsh AMs sun damu da' yin wauta '
Wasu AMs sun damu da shawarar canza taken su zuwa MWPs (Members of Welsh Parliament).
Wannan matsalar ta taso ne saboda shirye-shiryen canza sunan majalisa zuwa majalisar dokokin Wales.
AMs a duk faɗin siyasa sun nuna damuwa cewa za a yi wa wannan shawarar ba'a.
Wani ma'aikacin AM ya ce "yana da alaƙa da Twp da Pwp" wanda ya haifar da damuwa a cikin ƙungiyar su.
Ga masu karatu a waje da Wales: a cikin Welsh, twp yana nufin wauta kuma pwp yana nufin stool.
Wani mai suna Plaid AM ya ce kungiyar "ba ta da farin ciki" kuma ta ba da shawarar wasu sunaye.
Wani dan majalisa na Welsh ya ce kungiyarsa tana da "hankali" game da sauya sunan, amma ya ce kawai wani nau'i ne na Muppets ko wawa daga MWP.
A wannan yanayin, Yorkshire ta furta harafin Welsh w kamar yadda ake furta u a Turanci.
Hukumar da ke shirya dokar canja sunaye a yanzu ta ce: "Membobi ne za su yanke shawara a kan abin da za a kira 'yan majalisa".
Dokar Gwamnatin Wales ta 2017, ta ba wa majalisa na Wales ikon canza sunanta.
A watan Yuni, Hukumar ta wallafa wata sanarwa ta jama'a game da shawarwarin, wanda ya nuna cewa akwai goyon baya mai yawa ga majalisar dokokin da za a kira shi majalisar dokokin Wales.
Game da taken AMs, Hukumar ta fi son sunan 'yan majalisa na Welsh ko WMPs, amma sunan MWP ya sami goyon baya sosai.
Kamar yadda AMs ke ba da shawara game da zaɓuɓɓuka masu mahimmanci, amma yanke shawara ta hanyar yarjejeniya na iya zama ciwon kai ga Elin Jones, mai gudanarwa na yanzu. Ana sa ran Elin Jones zai gabatar da takaddar dokar game da canje-canje a cikin 'yan makonni.
Dokar kan gyare-gyare ta ƙunshi wasu canje-canje a cikin aikin Majalisar Dokoki, gami da ƙa'idodin hana AMs da tsarin tsarin kwamitin.
AMs suna da 'yancin yin zabe na ƙarshe a kan abin da za a kira su lokacin da ake tattaunawa game da doka.
