A cewar hasashen yanayi, guguwar Rosa tana ta sauka zuwa ruwan sanyi a gabar tekun arewacin Mexico.
Duk da haka, Rosa zai kawo ruwan sama mai yawa a duk faɗin arewacin Mexico da kudu maso yammacin Amurka a cikin kwanaki masu zuwa.
