LeBron zai fara wasan Lakers a San Diego ranar Lahadi.
A karshe dai an gama da fatan magoya baya game da wasan farko na LeBron James a Los Angeles Lakers.
Kocin Lakers Luke Walton ya sanar da cewa James zai buga wasan farko na kakar wasa ta biyu a ranar Lahadi da Denver Nuggets a San Diego.
Amma har yanzu ba a yanke shawarar tsawon lokacin da za su yi wasa ba.
"Wataƙila ya fi ɗaya amma ƙasa da 48", in ji Walton a shafin yanar gizon Lakers.
Mai ba da rahoto na Lakers Mike Trudell ya yi tweet cewa James zai iya yin wasa na iyakantaccen minti.
Bayan atisayen da aka yi a farkon wannan makon, an tambayi James game da shirinsa na wasannin Lakers na wasanni shida.
Ya ce, "A wannan lokacin na aiki, ba na bukatar wasannin Pre-Season don in shirya".
Trump ya yi jawabi a wani taron da aka yi a West Virginia, a tashar YouTube
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya fara gangamin yakin neman zabe a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko daga cikin gangamin gangamin biyar da aka tsara a mako mai zuwa, inda za su tsaya a wurare kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Bayan zabarsa don cike gurbin kotun koli, yanzu haka Trump yana son samun goyon baya saboda 'yan Republican na cikin hatsarin rasa iko a majalisar dokoki lokacin da za a gudanar da zaben tsakiyar watan Nuwamba.
Menene lokacin taron Trump na West Virginia a daren yau kuma ta yaya zaku iya kallon sa akan layi?
Trump ya yi jawabi a taron koli na West Virginia da yammacin karfe 7 na yamma.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump na West Virginia a kan layi a ƙasa ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube.
A wannan makon, Trump zai iya gabatar da wani taro game da sauraron kotun koli na Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya zama mai mahimmanci kuma ana sa ran dakatar da amincewa da kuri'un majalisar dattijai ga wanda aka bincika ta FBI game da cin zarafin jima'i.
Amma babban burin wannan gangamin shi ne karfafa gwiwar 'yan Republican a zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
Don haka, ana ganin kamfen din Shugaba Trump ne a matsayin masu ba da agaji da masu goyon baya don karfafawa masu aikin sa kai da masu goyon baya don karewa da fadada rinjaye da 'yan Republican ke da shi a majalisar dattijai da majalisa.
Wani kakakin yakin neman zaben Trump da ba a bayyana sunansa ba ya shaida wa Reuters cewa, saboda iko da majalisar dokoki yana da matukar muhimmanci a ajandarsa, Trump yana son shiga jihohi da dama kamar yadda zai iya, kuma hakan zai sa ya kasance cikin aiki a lokacin yakin neman zabe.
An shirya gangamin na yau da daddare a gidan wasan Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling, wanda zai iya gayyatar magoya bayan Ohio da Pennsylvania da kuma samun labaran kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh, West Virginia Metro News ta ruwaito.
A ranar Asabar ne Trump zai ziyarci jihar West Virginia karo na biyu cikin wata guda, inda ya lashe zaben da kashi 40 cikin 100 a shekarar 2016.
Trump ya yi kokarin taimaka wa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na West Virginia, Patrick Morris, wanda ya yi nasara a zaben.
Simon Haider, masanin kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, ya ce Trump ya zo don karfafawa a zaben ba kyakkyawan alama ba ne ga Morris.
