Ma'aurata ne kawai ba su yi harbi a ranar Asabar da rana ba, suna barin motar a ranar Asabar da safe, da yammacin Jumma'a kuma sun dawo gida da karfe tara na safe.
Wannan tseren da kuma makamashi da suke da shi ya nuna cewa 'yan wasan za su lashe wasan ranar Lahadi, kuma mutane sun goyi bayan hakan.
A cikin ramuka daban-daban a lokaci guda.
Ba daidai ba ne a yi magana game da nasarar Turai a yanzu.
Sergio Garcia ya yi aiki a cikin wasan kwaikwayo na safe lokacin da yake wasa da Alex Noreen.
A gaban tara, wani bogey da biyu biyu sun ƙarfafa Spaniard kuma ya zama mai zurfi ga rami kamar yadda ba zai yiwu ba.
A ranar Lahadi, babu wanda zai taimake ka ka fita daga cikin rami.
Abu ne mai ban sha'awa a ga Balls da Sums saboda sadarwa tsakanin ma'aurata da kuma shawarar da suke bayarwa da kuma shawarar da ba su bayar ba da kuma dabarun canzawa suna da mahimmanci.
Turai ta yi wasa sosai a matsayin ta kuma ta sami gagarumar nasara a ranar karshe. Amma, wannan zaman na hudu ya nuna cewa Team Amurka na da ikon yin gwagwarmayar da ake zargi.
Turai ta ci gaba da ci 10-6 a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup
Turai ta samu ci gaba mai kyau a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup bayan da ta ci gaba da 10-6 a kan Amurka a wasan kwallon kafa hudu da hudu a ranar Asabar.
An ƙarfafa su da Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari, sun sami nasara biyu a kan Tiger Woods, wanda ke neman daidaitawa da Talley, ya kai maki huɗu a Le Golf National.
Thomas Bjorn na Turai yana neman dawo da lambar yabo bayan ya rasa a Hazeltin shekaru biyu da suka gabata. Jerin ya kasance 3-1 saboda Amurka ta rasa wuta a wasan kwallon kafa na safe.
A gasar ta US Four Sam, sun yi tsayayya sosai, sun ci wasanni biyu, amma ba su iya magance matsalar ba.
Jim Furik yana bukatar maki takwas don riƙe da kyautar daga wasan 12 na Singles a ranar Lahadi.
Fleetwood ya zama farkon rookie na Turai da ya ci maki hudu a jere, kuma shi da Molinari, wanda ake kira Bollywood, sun zama biyu na biyu da suka ci maki hudu a farkon wasanni hudu a tarihin Ryder Cup bayan Weekend na ban mamaki.
Bayan sun doke Woods da Patrick Reed a Balls hudu, har yanzu rookie na Amurka Bryson DeChambeau ya doke Woods da 5-4 daga wani abin ban sha'awa.
Woods, wanda ya sha wahala a wasannin biyu a ranar Asabar, ya yi wasa sosai. Amma, ya rasa 19 daga cikin wasannin 29 a cikin Balls da Four Sum kuma ya rasa bakwai a jere.
Bayan sun huta a wasan kwallon kafa na safe, Justin Rose, Dustin Johnson da Brooks Kopkar sun yi nasara da Henrikh Stenson a wasan kwallon kafa na hudu da suka ci 2-1 kuma suna matsayi na daya da na uku a duniya.
