Wani sabon kwas da aka fara a Jami'ar Harvard a wannan shekarar, don magance al'adun maza da ke karuwa a karatun daliban da ke bacci sosai saboda maganin kafeyin.
Daliban da suka je jami'a mafi kyau a duniya ba su da wata fahimta ta yadda za su kula da kansu.
An tsara wannan kwas din ne ta hanyar Charles Seisler, Farfesa a Magungunan Barci a Harvard Medical School kuma kwararre ne a Brigham da asibitin mata, wanda ya yi imanin cewa wannan shine karo na farko da aka fara wannan kwas a Amurka.
Bayan ya yi jawabi game da tasirin rashin barci a kan ilmantarwa, ya sami wahayi zuwa wannan kwas.
'A ƙarshen, wata yarinya ta ce: 'Me ya sa ake gaya mini haka bayan shekaru da yawa, sa'ad da nake babban makaranta?'
Ta ce ba wanda ya taɓa gaya mata muhimmancin barci, abin da ya ba ni mamaki.
Wannan kwas din, wanda aka fara gudanarwa a wannan shekarar, zai bayyana wa dalibai yadda kyawawan halaye na bacci zasu taimaka wa nasarorin ilimi da wasanni, tare da inganta lafiyarsu.
Paul Barrera, Farfesa a fannin ilimin halayyar dan adam a Harvard Medical School kuma darektan zartarwa na ayyukan kiwon lafiya a Harvard Medical School, ya ce makarantar ta yanke shawarar gabatar da wannan kwas ne bayan da ta ga dalibai sun rasa barci a cikin mako.
Darussan da suka fi tsayi sun ƙunshi ayyuka masu ma'amala.
A wani sashe akwai hoto na ɗakin kwana, inda ɗalibai ke danna kan kofi, fuska, masu horarwa da littattafai don koyi game da tasirin maganin kafeyin da haske da kuma yadda rashin barci ke shafar wasanni da kuma muhimmancin lokacin barci.
A wani sashe kuma, an tattauna yadda rashin barci yake sa mutum ya yi ciwon zuciya, shanyewar jiki, baƙin ciki, da kuma ciwon daji.
