Jam'iyyar Jeremy Corbyn ta Labour tana tunanin wani tsari na asali wanda zai sa 'yan Birtaniya su yi aiki kwanaki hudu a mako - amma a biya su albashi na kwanaki biyar.
Jam'iyyar ta bukaci shugabannin kamfanoni su ba da tanadi da aka yi ta hanyar juyin juya halin Artificial Intelligence (AI) ta hanyar ba ma'aikata karin ranar hutu.
Wannan yana nuna cewa ma'aikata suna jin daɗin kwana uku - karshen mako - duk da haka suna karɓar adadin kuɗin da suke samu.
Majiyoyin sun ce, manufar ta yi daidai da ajandar tattalin arzikin jam'iyyar kuma tana shirin juyar da kasar a cikin fa'idar ma'aikata.
Ma'aikata sun amince da sauya zuwa kwanaki hudu a mako don amfani da tattalin arzikin da ke canzawa.
Wani babban jami'in jam'iyyar Labour ya shaida wa jaridar The Sunday Times cewa: 'Ana sa ran za a sanar da bita kan manufofin kafin karshen shekara.
'Ba za a yi irin wannan aikin ba dare daya amma aikin kwana hudu a mako shine hanyar jam'iyyar don daidaita tattalin arziki a madadin ma'aikata da kuma burin da ya dace da tsarin dabarun masana'antu na jam'iyyar.'
