Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da 'barazana' ta hanyar talla
Bayan da wata jaridar kasar Sin ta wallafa wani shafi hudu a wata jaridar Amurka da ke bayyana amfanin cinikayya tsakanin Sin da Amurka, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da amfani da kafofin yada labaran Amurka don cimma burinsa.
A ranar Laraba ne jaridar China ta bayyana a jaridar Des Moines Register, jaridar da ta fi sayarwa a Iowa, a matsayin wata dabara da Shugaba Donald Trump ya yi zargin cewa kasar Sin na kokarin yin tasiri a zaben majalisar dokokin Amurka da za a fara ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba.
Jami'an Amurka sun shaida wa Reuters cewa zargin da Trump ya yi cewa Beijing na kokarin yin tasiri a zaben Amurka wani bangare ne na kokarin matsa lamba kan China.
Gwamnatocin kasashen waje na amfani da jaridu wajen tallata kasuwanci, amma Beijing da Washington na cikin yakin cinikayya da ke ci gaba da kara haraji kan kayayyakin da suke sayarwa juna.
Masu kera kayayyaki a Sin da Amurka sun ce China ta sanya haraji kan masana'antun Amurka a hanyar da za ta baiwa masu fitar da kayayyaki a jihohi kamar Iowa, wadanda ke goyon bayan jam'iyyar Trump ta Republican.
Terry Brynstad, jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa, wanda kuma babban mai fitar da kayan gona ne ga kasar Sin, ya ce kasar Sin ta yi wa ma'aikata, manoma da kuma kasuwancin Amurka barazana.
A cikin jaridar Des Moines Register a ranar Lahadi, Brian Stad ya rubuta cewa, "China yanzu tana kokarin dafa wake ta hanyar tallatawa a jaridunmu na kyauta".
Brian Stead ya rubuta: "Tarihin 'yan jarida na Amurka ya ba da damar cinyewa a kasar Sin, kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin wani tallace-tallace a cikin Des Moines Register".
"A akasin wannan, idan ka ziyarci China a kan wani gidan jarida a kan titin Beijing, ba za ka ga wani ra'ayi game da matsalolin tattalin arzikin da kafofin watsa labarai ke yi ba, wanda ke ƙarƙashin ikon jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin", in ji shi.
"Wani babban jarida a ƙasar Sin ya yi jinkirin buga labarina", in ji shi, amma bai ambata sunan jaridar ba.
