An sake jinkirta sabon jirgin ruwan yaƙi na Jamus
An shirya tura sabon jirgin ruwan sojin ruwa na Jamus a shekarar 2014 don maye gurbin jiragen yakin Cold War, amma ba za a iya yin hakan ba har zuwa shekara mai zuwa saboda rashin ingantattun tsarin da farashin dusar ƙanƙara, in ji kafofin watsa labarai na gida.
A cewar jaridar Direct, tana ambaton kakakin soja, an dage ƙaddamar da sabon jirgin ruwa na Baden-Württemberg-class frigates "Rhineland-Pfalz" zuwa farkon rabin 2019.
An shirya jirgin ya shiga cikin rundunar sojan ruwa a shekarar 2014, amma wasu matsaloli bayan bayarwa sun lalata makomar wannan babban shiri.
Jiragen ruwa guda hudu na Baden-Wuerttemberg da aka sake yin oda a 2007 za su maye gurbin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
An san cewa sun ƙunshi manyan bindigogi, da kewayon makamai masu linzami da na jirgin ruwa, da kuma wasu fasahohin ɓoye kamar ƙananan radar, infrared da sautin sauti.
Sauran manyan fasalulluka sun hada da tsawon lokacin aiki, wato, yiwuwar tura sabbin jiragen ruwa daga manyan tashoshin jiragen ruwa na gida har tsawon shekaru biyu.
Duk da haka, saboda jinkirin da ake yi na jiragen ruwa na zamani - wanda aka ce zai ba Jamus damar yin amfani da wutar lantarki a kasashen waje - Dirkts ya ce za su riga sun tsufa a lokacin da suka shiga sabis.
A bayyane yake cewa jirgin yakin F125 ya yi labarai a bara ta hanyar hana shi zama jirgin ruwa na Jamus a matsayin jirgin ruwa na Jamus kuma ya koma gidan jirgin ruwa na Blohm da Voss a Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da rundunar sojan ruwa ta dawo da jirgin ruwa ga maginin jirgin ruwa bayan an kawo shi.
Ba a san dalilin da ya sa aka dawo ba, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun ambaci cewa akwai wasu dalilai masu mahimmanci game da "rashin software da kayan aiki" wanda zai sa jirgin ya zama mara amfani idan an tura shi cikin yaki.
Sakamakon rashin amfani da software na iya zama babban tasiri saboda ana amfani da jiragen ruwa na Baden-Württemberg na kimanin 120 na jiragen ruwa - wanda ke amfani da rabin ma'aikata idan aka kwatanta da tsohuwar jirgin ruwa na Bremen.
Har ila yau, jirgin yana da nauyin nauyi wanda zai rage aikinsa kuma ya iyakance ikon Navy don ƙarawa a nan gaba.
An yi imanin cewa "Rhineland-Pfalz" mai nauyin tan 7,000 ya ninka nauyin jirage masu kama da na Jamus a yakin duniya na biyu.
Baya ga kayan aiki mara kyau, farashin duk aikin - gami da horar da ma'aikata - yana zama matsala.
An ce an fara shi ne daga €2.2 biliyan zuwa €3.1 biliyan ($3.6 biliyan).
Wadannan matsaloli sun zama masu mahimmanci musamman game da samun sabbin jiragen ruwa a karkashin sabon gargadi cewa sojojin ruwa a Jamus suna raguwa.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Hans-Peter Bartels, shugaban kwamitin kare dangi na majalisar dokokin Jamus, ya yarda cewa sojojin ruwa suna "fitar da jiragen ruwa masu aiki".
Jami'in ya ce matsalar ta kara girma kamar dusar ƙanƙara a tsawon lokaci, saboda an soke tsofaffin jiragen ruwa amma ba a samar da sabbin jiragen ruwa ba.
Ya yi nadamar cewa babu wani jirgin ruwa na Baden-Württemberg da zai iya sake shiga cikin jirgin ruwa.
