Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara dole ne su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe mutane takwas da gangan kuma ya haifar da mummunan rauni, a cewar sanarwar niyyar neman hukuncin kisa, wanda aka shigar a gundumar New South Wales.
A cewar kotun, duka biyun suna da hukuncin kisa.
Makonni bayan harin, wani babban alkalin kotun tarayya ya tuhumi Saipov da laifin aikata laifuka 22, wanda ya hada da laifuka takwas na kisan kai tare da taimakon 'yan fashi, wanda yawanci masu gabatar da kara na tarayya ke amfani da su a cikin laifukan aikata laifuka da kuma lalata motoci.
Wannan harin ya bukaci "shirye-shiryen da aka yi da kuma shiri mai kyau", masu gabatar da kara sun bayyana yadda aka yi a Saipov a matsayin "mummunan, zalunci da yaudara".
"Saifullo Habillavich Sipov ya yi rauni da asara ga iyalai da abokai na Diego Enrique Angelín, Nicholas Cleaves, Anne-Laure Decadette, Darren Drake, Ariel Erliz, Hernan Ferrucci, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damián Pagunanuco.
