An kashe mutum na karshe a wani shari'ar tarayya a New York a 1953 bayan da aka kashe wani ma'aurata, Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, shekaru biyu da suka gabata bayan da suka yi niyyar yin coci ga Soviet Union a lokacin Cold War.
An kashe Rosenberg da kuma sauran 'yan uwansa biyu a kan kujera ta lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
