Yadda Yakin Ciniki na Amurka da China ya Amfane Beijing
Yakin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China ba ya yin sauti a yau, kuma masana sun bayyana ra'ayin cewa, ko da yake yakin ya yi nisa, rikice-rikice tsakanin kasashen na iya zama da amfani ga Beijing a cikin dogon lokaci.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya ba da gargadin farko a farkon wannan shekarar ta hanyar sanya haraji kan manyan kayayyakin da ake fitarwa daga China, ciki har da bangarorin hasken rana, karfe da aluminium.
