Beijing ma ta yi ramuwar gayya a kan wannan a kowane lokaci, kwanan nan ta sanya haraji tsakanin kashi biyar zuwa goma bisa dari kan kayayyakin Amurka biliyan 60.
China ta yi alkawarin cewa za ta hada kai da Amurka, kuma tattalin arzikin duniya na biyu ba zai ragu ba da jimawa ba.
Komawa Washington baya yana nufin zama abin da ake buƙata, amma yin biyayya ga Amurka a fili yana da matukar damuwa ga shugaban China Xi Jinping.
Koyaya, masana sun ce idan Beijing ta sami damar yin wasan ta yadda ya kamata, matsin lamba daga yakin kasuwancin Amurka zai taimaka wa China cikin dogon lokaci ta hanyar rage dogaro tsakanin tattalin arzikin biyu.
