A gasar golf da aka yi a Le Golf National a bayan birnin Paris, Faransa, Team Turai ta doke Team USA da 16.5 zuwa 10.5 kuma ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup ta 2018.
Amurka yanzu ta yi rashin nasara sau shida a jere a Turai kuma ba ta lashe Ryder Cup a Turai ba tun 1993.
Dan wasan Danish din Thomas Jørn ya sake lashe kofin Turai yayin da tawagarsa ta kai maki 14.5 da ake bukata don doke tawagar Amurka.
Tauraron Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya yi fama da rashin tsari a mafi yawan gasar, ya yi ruwa a kan rami na 16 na Par-3 wanda ya rasa wasan da Francesco Molinari.
Molinari, wani dan wasan golf na Italiya, ya yi haske a duk zagaye, yana daya daga cikin 'yan wasan 4 da suka ci 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara gasar a shekarar 1979.
