Red Tide Update: Yawan algae yana raguwa a cikin Pinellas, Manate da Sarasota
Wani sabon rahoto daga Hukumar Kifi da Daji ta Florida ya nuna cewa yawan Red Tide yana nuna raguwa a wasu sassan yankin Tampa Bay.
A cewar FWC, an bayar da rahoton yanayin fashewar fure a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier Counties - wanda ke nuna cewa yawan yana raguwa.
